8d-0ab0-4303-8b2c-c3ecca87767e\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>□ 생각하신 종이가 있나요?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0d80073a-c3c1-400e-9bb5-8a0ba8834720\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7c498cf9-707f-47fe-bba7-dcc0fea0dab0\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a4adbedd-1a71-4378-bb29-ff7ea529e151\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-06d3a797-a13b-48ce-90f2-28bcfd55fb50\" style=\"color:#555555;\">리플렛에 사용하는 종이는 다양합니다. 일반용지에서 고급 용지까지 다양하여 선택의 폭이 넓습니다. 일반적으로는 아트지/스노우지가 있고 고급지로는 반누브나 랑데뷰, 아르떼 용지 등이 있습니다. 다만 수입지의 경우 UV 인쇄로 뒷묻음을 방지해야 하는 경우가 있어 단가가 비싸질 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2de21236-5b8a-4651-9b56-04cd99946743\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-88f9e014-0c58-407e-9f61-f9dd5bbb9e9b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f1cc8e86-6e9b-496a-8b76-a71954903cc7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-399cd69c-f0e4-49d1-8524-72f62825dc4f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-695b4fa2-c335-4692-a7f0-8ae718fa9e12\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-202667e5-230e-4973-9493-32e7b3a024b0\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>□ 사이즈와 수량은?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bf61f7a4-ba58-454d-9910-41a2c81cc663\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-95b2213d-d124-4320-8abd-38caeac49a01\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-83eac179-64e3-4ca2-83af-fd2168c4f67c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1ae664d6-f41d-4af9-8622-55a82bde23e4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">리플렛 발주에서 중요한 것이 사이즈입니다. 소통에서 혼동이 되는 것이 접었을 때 A4? 펼쳤을 때 A4등으로 차이가 있습니다. A4를 접어서 만들 것인가? 아니면 접어서 최종 결과물이 A4인가에 따라 견적이 달라집니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d0e1537d-3fde-4d02-9baa-8c6fe7a91db8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-507e3750-b8bf-42ea-996e-1a487c5d6660\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-231bbfb3-bb4b-43e2-9681-76664e26bfd5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-be037871-962a-4422-8626-5aa8970790cc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">또한 디지털은 기본 수량 같은 것은 없습니다. 1장부터 가능합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e020122b-b137-40ac-95b9-b96ecac6ef45\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-74a3a21f-2f4e-4a63-b704-a50f6b119e10\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ac41b1a6-b151-4b9b-a48e-ee8546cc49cc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-df176736-107b-4b0e-a7cb-7513f7355dd9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2168cac4-bb68-489f-bd99-b9d9be2eb62a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-12751115-3cc0-4ce6-bbb9-a6017fe5b636\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>□ 접지? 코팅?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4bcc4233-6aeb-4e22-ba44-e7c1dda49932\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2da57137-51e3-42ac-b217-86788ed7c746\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1b688411-c02b-4059-9ea3-70b2a3f02130\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-38f977e3-30c0-424f-8dbe-010a311fb237\" style=\"color:#555555;\">납기를 좌우하는 것이 후공정입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-616d31ac-e176-498f-9e55-addb8aab72e1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4570a0d1-bd08-4861-97c9-0a1fa4c63953\" style=\"color:#555555;\">후공정이 많을수록 납기는 지연되지만 가능한 익일로 납기를 맞추려고 하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-28431f69-0db3-4e55-950d-0fcea34bd80c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6c2b7a87-9ea8-4135-b550-99e4621453f5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e22f38a2-3819-412c-b5f3-aade41110421\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-177b8feb-2e42-4713-b64a-2cf794759fdd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">후공정이 있는 리플렛은 반드시 상담을 통해 납기를 확인하고 주문하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-64cbb075-3245-4824-aff3-09ab9dc8a105\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ca58c96c-6501-4f9a-a1de-260d76718c2e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c90bf737-b99b-476e-a080-23c9adbc1d8a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-33b15c2f-fdac-43f5-a9a7-303c694aad3b\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">이제 급한 리플렛은 (주)파파스컴퍼니에 주문하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3429c332-da5f-4fe5-b485-3ea2ca565aff\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-74c02655-a470-4bc4-9812-ae57dddc634a\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1418b90c-befd-4fc1-8b9e-69500b0bf9bc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F223871116833#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
